            <p>
                The Seongbuk-gu government, as the 7th democratically elected administration, will become a government that works closely with its people and one that cares deeply for the lives of every resident. It will always be by the side of its citizens, and do its best to bring positive changes across Seongbuk-gu that can be felt by each and every resident. And to do so, the Seongbuk-gu government hopes to improve its communication with the public, pursue better policies, and protect fundamental values and principles in all areas of the district’s administration. <br /><br />

